{
  "sn12.48:0.1": "Saṁyutta Nikāya 12.48 ",
  "sn12.48:0.2": "5. Gahapativagga ",
  "sn12.48:0.3": "Lokāyatikasutta ",
  "sn12.48:1.1": "Sāvatthiyaṁ viharati. ",
  "sn12.48:1.2": "Atha kho lokāyatiko brāhmaṇo yena bhagavā …pe… ",
  "sn12.48:1.3": "ekamantaṁ nisinno kho lokāyatiko brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṁ etadavoca: ",
  "sn12.48:2.1": "“Kiṁ nu kho, bho gotama, sabbamatthī”ti? ",
  "sn12.48:2.2": "“‘Sabbamatthī’ti kho, brāhmaṇa, jeṭṭhametaṁ lokāyataṁ”. ",
  "sn12.48:3.1": "“Kiṁ pana, bho gotama, sabbaṁ natthī”ti? ",
  "sn12.48:3.2": "“‘Sabbaṁ natthī’ti kho, brāhmaṇa, dutiyametaṁ lokāyataṁ”. ",
  "sn12.48:4.1": "“Kiṁ nu kho, bho gotama, sabbamekattan”ti? ",
  "sn12.48:4.2": "“‘Sabbamekattan’ti kho, brāhmaṇa, tatiyametaṁ lokāyataṁ”. ",
  "sn12.48:5.1": "“Kiṁ pana, bho gotama, sabbaṁ puthuttan”ti? ",
  "sn12.48:5.2": "“‘Sabbaṁ puthuttan’ti kho, brāhmaṇa, catutthametaṁ lokāyataṁ. ",
  "sn12.48:6.1": "Ete te, brāhmaṇa, ubho ante anupagamma majjhena tathāgato dhammaṁ deseti: ",
  "sn12.48:6.2": "‘avijjāpaccayā saṅkhārā; ",
  "sn12.48:6.3": "saṅkhārapaccayā viññāṇaṁ …pe… ",
  "sn12.48:6.4": "evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa samudayo hoti. ",
  "sn12.48:6.5": "Avijjāya tveva asesavirāganirodhā saṅkhāranirodho; ",
  "sn12.48:6.6": "saṅkhāranirodhā viññāṇanirodho …pe… ",
  "sn12.48:6.7": "evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hotī’”ti. ",
  "sn12.48:7.1": "Evaṁ vutte, lokāyatiko brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṁ etadavoca: ",
  "sn12.48:7.2": "“abhikkantaṁ, bho gotama …pe… ",
  "sn12.48:7.3": "ajjatagge pāṇupetaṁ saraṇaṁ gatan”ti. ",
  "sn12.48:7.4": "Aṭṭhamaṁ. "
}